      },
      "date": "2020-02-12 22:29:28.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nI tested with tag: Ubuntu-5.3.0-29.31\n\nshaun@eoan:~/ubuntu/eoan$ git diff Makefile\ndiff --git a/Makefile b/Makefile\nindex c05b78960261..47817227102e 100644\n--- a/Makefile\n+++ b/Makefile\n@@ -1,8 +1,8 @@\n # SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-2.0\n VERSION = 5\n PATCHLEVEL = 3\n-SUBLEVEL = 13\n-EXTRAVERSION =\n+SUBLEVEL = 0\n+EXTRAVERSION = -29-generic\n NAME = Bobtail Squid\n \n # *DOCUMENTATION*\n\n\nFYI \"-29-generic\" had me a circles for a while as my older notes suggested without the dash prefix.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
