      },
      "date": "2020-02-14 22:51:22.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nNote that if you find some wonky issues with QUOTA with this patch is\nis due to the bug in the ext4-data-in-dirent.patch\nIn ext4.h it *should* be:\n  #define EXT4_MOUNT_DIRDATA\t0x60000\t/* Data in directory entries*/\n\nBut the current patch is using:\n  #define EXT4_MOUNT_DIRDATA\t0x40000\t/* Data in directory entries*/\n\nWill be pushing a fix RSN",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
